Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}策謀的宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在確認識別碼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝特中尉的小隊正在急速趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是要參加這次閱艦式的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兩天後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自一年戰爭以來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的高官們也總算是伸夠懶腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閱艦式是以前就預定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦原來也應作為新銳艦參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚會議強制舉行閱艦式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是想顯示聯邦的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我並不認為那些傢伙會寧事息人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個阿納貝爾·卡多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是貝特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目測目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰艦伯明翰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺逍遙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀閱旗艦居然沒帶護衛艦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀閱官應該是格林·懷亞特大將吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的MS是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是阿爾比昂派出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘不懂得變通的船嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丟下遲鈍的Cannon不管了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Cannon：這裏指GM Cannon，RX-77-2 Guncannon的量產機\N為降低成本採用了RGM-79的框架、裝甲等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪費太多子彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話也太多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞過來了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於贏了大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打贏大尉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實戰的話你已被擊落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是打得快活點吧，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去請你喝啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠Full Burnern的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是靠我技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已能運用它了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已是個老頭了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知還能乘它多久啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有黑色物體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大！很大！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是聯絡過的太空殖民地的移送嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有殖民地大小的實感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把戰禍中受損SIDE1的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送到SIDE3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是殖民地再生計劃的第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…太空殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於擊落了巴寧格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究的成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況預測很直接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架GUNDAM會成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著某位先生的戰技等級一起成長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我的GUNDAM嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我們的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候從「在下」改口成「我」了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對聯邦的軍官請別擺出大姐的架子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話等你敢吃胡蘿蔔了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的GUNDAM就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這陣子太疲勞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的話配點維生素給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是怎麼回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳骨折時還到處逃避治療的大尉卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是腳在一直叫我快逃快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是愛耍嘴皮子，證明很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,診斷完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不適？大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長您難道…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被限制酒量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被醫生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天喝到這個刻度為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，得讓我多喝一個刻度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾陪我喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酒一個人喝也沒滋味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都吃得下這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是男子漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妮娜老是把我當小孩子看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然，就算在絕大部分的少爺中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍是最優秀的純粹培養啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}純粹培養：把生物從其他種類生物中分離出來\N只培養一個種類或一個系統的科學技術，主要用於微生物的培養
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我不是來談這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒙夏中尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀戀不捨，還在做這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摩拉在GM的駕駛艙裏發現的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧，這張很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼拍到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妮娜小姐有時確實會散發出嫵媚的芳香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是表現出拍照的蒙夏中尉的下流而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真急死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不懂嗎？那成熟的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有GUNDAM做你的愛神丘比特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的是你和她能不能順利進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡她吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不想更瞭解女性嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到腳地瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小伙子如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在紮實地成長著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試機師領悟得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有妮娜的支持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使除去這個因素進步也很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公私雙方面好像都受到她照顧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來人事制度也有重新檢討的餘地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是以勝利為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在地球上有位夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等作戰告一段落就申請休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說他們有了成長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是能和年輕人逞強的年紀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是心態上的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然這麼說了也不勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與妻子以前就處於分居狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是…失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想以機師的身份與迪拉茲戰鬥到最後而沒有懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦即將與補給艦會合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也暫時去睡一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想念啊，卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,302巡哨中隊如今僅剩下3架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心就像現在的宇宙一樣振奮著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也發生了奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於希瑪中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們差點就誤降在希瑪艦隊上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪·格拉罕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她負責的應該是其它方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到達Z地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的那些傢伙會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的不是狐就是貍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到會合地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝大吉嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}大吉嶺：產於印度孟加拉省的大吉嶺一帶的極品紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給艦艾治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊特中尉以下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求著艦許可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准許
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到阿爾比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回還有郵件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民的阿納海姆的巴普爾頓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蒙夏中尉那色鬼一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片全都在宏那傢伙手裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種偷窺狂的照片，你賣了多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂女人心的臭傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎麼搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相、相信我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，從實招來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須去值班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老實交代的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那些都丟進碎紙機了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜眼說瞎話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在看這種書的他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會做那種事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《女性的知識ABC》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《宇宙住民女性論》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《女體的神秘》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在看什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木、吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值班怎麼辦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，這是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的鬆懈會讓船沉沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再教訓你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經米諾夫斯基幹涉波的反探測測知疑似戰艦的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5-1-9
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伯明翰的附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的出動如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就出動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫貝特他們也準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為女士總要別人等待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是海軍陸戰隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉看來也有點棘手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士都喜歡禮物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是定律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂的緊急來電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們發現敵艦影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已派MS急速趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發信 阿爾比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受信 觀閱艦隊司令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確像高雲麾下的艦隻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反轉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯明翰反轉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出賣我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別慌張！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼貝倫格沉沒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要讓我逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在做戲給友軍看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒打中這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是個好男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是伯明翰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逃離時還擊沉了一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2時方向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2艘逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是掩護伯明翰撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被修理了還不學乖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別浪費彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在貝特中尉他們到達之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要利用形勢！浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在、在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就該躲起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人，差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人估計也有增援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道，我還不想找死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對3架敵機仍一邊倒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、有一架沒在動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢就交給巴格曼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣或許
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能瞭解敵人的戰力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想從我希瑪的買賣裏抽成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉·瑪蓮到了回收的極限距離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正會有麻煩的人是卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了一下彈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾比昂很近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥配置解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把貝特他們的小隊也叫回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊落敵MS兩架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是巴寧格大尉的戰績
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司考特，能接通嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊，巴寧格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我還有另一個戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸艦後立刻向你匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可要好好期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊前的事我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就暫且原諒他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎是太鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然伯明翰沒受損
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果出擊得太遲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從摩拉那聽說了事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒙夏那傢伙拍的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張也沒留？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個多疑的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會被當做孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已能獨當一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也和敵人勢均力敵地戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往後就看你們是否能切實體會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我無法教的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話以前也說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜色中的澳大利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得做俯臥撐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也該留下一張的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉也帶著那種東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不至於像你那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說教結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在著艦前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基於海軍令則
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星塵作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門海域實施綱要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方的配置一目瞭然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2號機？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:22:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡多嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多要行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這、這是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴寧格大尉！！
