Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西爾維亞·巴寧格…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.11,0:25:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夫人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊前沒能交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.62,0:25:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來回信吧
